text: Chad Morgan (born September 21, 1973) is an American actress best known for her voice-over work on Adult Swim's Robot Chicken, where she voices celebrities. ==Celebrities voiced== This is a list of celebrities Morgan has voiced and/or impersonated. * Gillian Anderson (as Dana Scully from The X-Files) * Laura Bush * Hilary Clinton * Katie Couric * Cameron Diaz * Florence Henderson (as Carol Brady from The Brady Bunch) * Daryl Hannah (as Elle Driver from Kill Bill Vol. 1) * Hilary Duff * Estelle Getty (as Sophia Petrillo from The Golden Girls * Teri Hatcher * Paris Hilton * Maureen McCormick (from Marcia Brady from The Brady Bunch) * Ashley Olsen * Betsy McCaughey * J.K. Rowling * Ashlee Simpson * Tiffani Thiessen (as Kelly Kapowski from Saved by the Bell) * Christina Aguilera * Jamie Lynn Spears ==Other websites== * Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from Atlanta Category:American television actors
title: Chad Morgan (actress)
